title: Hummus Republic
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Assembly-line Mediterranean cuisine bar, offering 3 daily hummus plus salads with your choice of dressing, create-your-own pita. Has a seitan EarthBurger, and falafel burger, vegan soup. Need to specify if you're vegan.
